title.rendered: STEDI TALL TYPE RJ45 UHF PASS THROUGH TO SUIT TOYOTA

content.rendered:
RJ45 pass through connector to suit Toyota vehicle

 

 

 

DETAILS

RJ45 pass through connector This RJ45 pass through connector allows for a UHF fitted with an RJ45 connector to be plugged in.

COMPATIBLE TOYOTA MAKES

  • Toyota Hilux| KUN26R, GGN15R, GGN25R 2005  to 2014
  • Toyota Landcruiser 100 Series | 1998 to 2007
  • Toyota Prado 120 Series | 2003 – 2009
  • Toyota Landcruiser 75, 76, 78 & 79 Series
  • Toyota FJ Cruiser | 2010 to Current
  • Toyota Hiace 2005-2013

SPECIFICATIONS

BACK LIGHT COLOUR Blue
SURFACE SIZE DIMENSIONS 39mmx21mm

 

WHAT’S IN THE BOX

  • Toyota Tall UHF RJ45 Pass-through
